    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinite Idle：在线点击式角色扮演游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对数十种不同的敌人和老板，他们永远不会放弃！这场战斗将永远持续下去。准备好每次都做出更好的决定。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/76d53b19eb3f2ae39efe4f9440b3d207.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>从数十种不同的选择中做出最佳决定。会有惊喜的礼物和帮手给你，别忘了使用它们。记住，你不能把金子带回家。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/16fcc9361c54304a506dab3c025d0809.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>利用你的特殊能力，用好的策略克服无法逾越的困难。即使你不在场，战斗仍在继续。别忘了这一点！当你在场时，你总是更强大。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.poster.avif?t=1732227172\" width=572 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.webm?t=1732227172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197860/extras/1d3703f17b17108f744cbbc0bd40fd52.mp4?t=1732227172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
